        <div class="resources-col">
            <p>Normally you wouldn’t put Bible Study, golf, art, and motorcycles together, but those are a few of the things I most enjoy.</p>
            <p>I love the Word of God and sharing the unsearchable riches of Christ with my people. I’m not a very good golfer and have learned to enjoy it in spite of my ineptitude.</p>
            <p>Art is another area in which my love exceeds my ability. I’ve done a few pieces that could never attain the standard I hold as to what constitutes "fine art". My Harley-Davidson is a 2001 Fatboy 1340 V-Twin, that I love to take out on sunny days and on short trips.</p>
            <p>Listed below you’ll find my recommendations for of few of the resources that I know, use, and love.</p>
        </div>

